 DemoNuGridLongCell connected;F;values;cellTypes;rowTitles;colTitles;n;longText
 EWC.CONNECTEDв†ђconnected
 вҺ•PWв†ђ1000

вҚқ Reported issue: in a NuGrid with a large dataset where a cell's content
вҚқ is too long to fit, clicking on an editable cell shows the blue selection
вҚқ outline only spanning roughly half the cell width.
вҚқ This demo exercises both conditions (many rows + long values + wide cells)
вҚқ across several layouts so we can see whether the selection border really
вҚқ underspans the cell.

 Fв†ђ'F1'
 F eWC'Form' 'NuGrid Long-Cell Selection Repro'(50 50)(900 1500)('Coord' 'Pixel')

 nв†ђ60
 longTextв†ђ'A very long product description that does not fit inside the visible portion of the cell at all'

вҚқ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Grid A: large dataset, wide cells, very long text в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
вҚқ Hypothesis: with cell content wider than the visible cell width and many
вҚқ rows scrolling vertically, the blue selection border may render only on
вҚқ the visible portion (left half) of the cell.
 (F,'.LA')eWC'Label' 'A: 60 rows, wide cells (300px), long text values'(60 30)(24 700)
 (F,'.GA')eWC'NuGrid'('Posn'(90 30))('Size'(260 700))('CellWidths'(300 300 100))('CurCell'(1 1))('VScroll' ВҮ1)('HScroll' ВҮ1)
 valuesAв†ђn 3вҚөвЉ‚''
 valuesA[;1]в†ђ{longText,' #',вҚ•вҚµ}ВЁвҚіn              вҚқ long text per row
 valuesA[;2]в†ђ{'Short ',вҚ•вҚµ}ВЁвҚіn                   вҚқ short text
 valuesA[;3]в†ђвҚіn                                  вҚқ numeric
 (F,'.GA')eWS('Values' valuesA)('CellTypes'(n 3вҚө1 1 2))
 (F,'.GA')eWS'ColTitles'('Long Description' 'Short' 'Qty')
 (F,'.GA')eWS'RowTitles'(вҚіn)
 (F,'.GA.E1')eWC'Edit'
 (F,'.GA.E2')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')
 (F,'.GA')eWS'Input'((F,'.GA.E1')(F,'.GA.E2'))

вҚқ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Grid B: same data as A but smaller cell width (60 px) в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
вҚқ Cells too narrow to fit any of the text content; ellipsis kicks in.
вҚқ Click a cell to see whether the selection outline still spans the full
вҚқ visible td width or only part of it.
 (F,'.LB')eWC'Label' 'B: same data, narrow cells (60px) вЂ” ellipsis everywhere'(440 30)(24 700)
 (F,'.GB')eWC'NuGrid'('Posn'(470 30))('Size'(260 283))('CellWidths'(60 60 60))('CurCell'(1 1))('VScroll' ВҮ1)('HScroll' ВҮ1)
 (F,'.GB')eWS('Values' valuesA)('CellTypes'(n 3вҚө1 1 2))
 (F,'.GB')eWS'ColTitles'('Long Description' 'Short' 'Qty')
 (F,'.GB')eWS'RowTitles'(вҚіn)
 (F,'.GB.E1')eWC'Edit'
 (F,'.GB.E2')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')
 (F,'.GB')eWS'Input'((F,'.GB.E1')(F,'.GB.E2'))

вҚқ в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ Grid C: mixed widths to bracket the boundary в”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђв”Ђ
вҚқ One narrow column next to one wide column, varying long content.
вҚқ Placed in its own column on the right with extra padding.
 (F,'.LC')eWC'Label' 'C: mixed widths (50 / 350 / 80) вЂ” click each col to compare'(60 800)(24 600)
 (F,'.GC')eWC'NuGrid'('Posn'(90 800))('Size'(342 583))('CellWidths'(50 350 80))('CurCell'(1 1))('VScroll' ВҮ1)('HScroll' ВҮ1)
 valuesCв†ђ20 3вҚөвЉ‚''
 valuesC[;1]в†ђвҚі20
 valuesC[;2]в†ђ{longText,' row=',вҚ•вҚµ}ВЁвҚі20
 valuesC[;3]в†ђвҚі20
 (F,'.GC')eWS('Values' valuesC)('CellTypes'(20 3вҚө2 1 2))
 (F,'.GC')eWS'ColTitles'('#' 'Long Description' 'Qty')
 (F,'.GC')eWS'RowTitles'(вҚі20)
 (F,'.GC.E1')eWC'Edit'
 (F,'.GC.E2')eWC'Edit'('FieldType' 'Numeric')
 (F,'.GC')eWS'Input'((F,'.GC.E1')(F,'.GC.E2'))
